    <p><b>GE Profile</b> — premium $1.5-5k tier, feature-focused with True European Convection + SmartHQ Wi-Fi + Air Fry. Competes with Samsung + LG + KitchenAid.</p>
    <p><b>GE Café</b> — style-first premium $2.5-8k tier, Matte Black/White finishes + customizable hardware. Competes with Samsung Bespoke + LG STUDIO at aesthetic-first positioning.</p>
    <p>All three lines route parts through the same Haier-owned GE Appliances distribution in Louisville Kentucky. For LA customers with mixed GE-family kitchens — Monogram wall oven + Profile range + Café refrigerator, a common premium renovation pattern — the unified parts-chain supports single-dispatch service across the whole kitchen.</p>
